data.description: Beautifully designed home on the Northeast side that is moments from downtown and easy access to nearby freeways.  This home features recessed lighting, luxury laminate plank flooring, quartz counters, built in wine rack, new cabinets, herringbone backsplash tile, under cabinet lighting, gorgeous remodeled master bathroom, new fixtures, paint, texture, and so much more. Stand out with a custom made walnut epoxy barn door! The fourth bedroom has its own half bath which could also be used as a second den/game room/ study.
